Locust rangers are encountered during the Dealing with Scabaras quest. They can be used to get Scabarite notes for the Scabarites Notes miniquest, and also for the Scabarites slayer assignment. Protect from Missiles may be needed as they are aggressive. Their attacks are slow, but accurate, and have a max hit of 210.

Locations[edit | edit source]

Location Levels Members Requirements Spawns Map
Ullek77None1Maplink

The area is considered part desert, and the player may require water (or Enchanted water tiara) due the desert heat effect. Three tiles south of the statue, and all north of this line, are desert areas. Staying south of this line will negate the desert heat effect.
